<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>164</hymn_number>
<author>George L. Williams</author>
<aka>Trust in Jesus.</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Afoha bilia yokʋt
 Chisʋs ak banoshke:
 Si okchalinchit illi tok,
 Ahni li banoshke.

[V2]
 Chu̱kʋsh achukma ʋma cha,
 Chimmi ish ikbashke;
 Chu̱kʋsh achukma ʋma cha,
 Ʋmmi ish tobashke.

[V3]
 Si Okchalinchi Chisʋs ma!
 Ai ashʋchi li ya̱
 Chim issish holitopa ya̱
 Isht ish kashoffashke.

[V4]
 Hatak moma ʋlhtoba hosh
 Issish ish ima tok;
 Yohmi tok a̱ na̱ pi yimmit
 E pisa pullashke.</lyrics>
<title>Afoha bilia yokʋt ƲIT164</title>
<time_sig>C.M. (8.6.8.6.)</time_sig>
</song>